Instruct the Municipal Treasurer to ensure timely collection of monthly rental fees, otherwise, penalties should be imposed and collected for late payments;
Include in the Contract with the Lessee terms on security deposit/guarantee to insure the government from losses;
Determine the amount of electric and water consumptions of the Variety Store from August 2020 to December 2022, Restaurant from August 2022 to December 2022 and Two-Storey Building for CY 2022 and collect the same from the Lessees, otherwise, a Notice of Disallowance will be issued for the electric and water expenses at the GRHR, which were paid by the LGU; and
