The Management agreed to adhere with the audit recommendations.
Auditor’s Rejoinder:
The Audit Team will issue the Notice of Charge amounting to P800,000.00 and a Notice of Disallowance for electric and water consumption from CY 2020 to CY 2022 at GRHR if the Management fails to collect the same from the Lessees.

